07:22.000 --> 07:26.000
Other people are oriented to the future.

07:26.000 --> 07:32.000
What will I achieve if I implement these or other positions?

07:32.000 --> 07:36.000
Not now, not in the past, what will my future be?

07:36.000 --> 07:40.000
And when you come to him with a contract, where everything is calculated,

07:40.000 --> 07:43.000
