07:50.000 --> 07:52.000
And what will be in the future?

07:52.000 --> 07:55.000
And you are not prepared to give this future picture.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
You start to improvise, and so on.

07:57.000 --> 08:04.000
And the negotiations, not that it goes into a deadlock, but the parties remain dissatisfied.

08:04.000 --> 08:06.000
You brought me all the information.

08:06.000 --> 08:09.000
Other people are oriented to the present.

08:09.000 --> 08:15.000
The past is already there, the future is not there yet, and it is not known whether it will be there.

08:15.000 --> 08:17.000
But the present is there.

08:17.000 --> 08:23.000
You came to me, and, accordingly, your company, my company is interested in you,

08:23.000 --> 08:26.000
your company is interested in cooperating with ours.

08:26.000 --> 08:28.000
This is today.

08:28.000 --> 08:32.000
And, accordingly, I do not need to build an air castle, which I will be in the future.

08:32.000 --> 08:35.000
I need to talk about how good it was in the past.

08:35.000 --> 08:41.000
What will change for me today, if I implement your contract?

08:41.000 --> 08:43.000
This is the time orientation.

08:43.000 --> 08:49.000
It often disappears, and, by the way, very often leads to a misunderstanding of people with each other.

08:49.000 --> 08:52.000
Someone is talking about the future,

08:52.000 --> 08:58.000
and the other is worried about the problems that are now following him, which he needs to solve.

08:59.000 --> 09:03.000
Someone is worried about the current situation.

09:03.000 --> 09:09.000
He is interested in the fact that today he needs to transfer a certain payment, but there is no money.

09:09.000 --> 09:12.000
Yes, they may be tomorrow, but today I do not transfer.

09:12.000 --> 09:15.000
Yes, they were yesterday, but today I do not have.

09:15.000 --> 09:18.000
Therefore, the time orientation is such a painful thing.

09:18.000 --> 09:20.000
24 hours a day.

09:20.000 --> 09:22.000
We all live in the present.

09:22.000 --> 09:26.000
Each of us has a future that we want, and there is a past,

09:26.000 --> 09:29.000
in which there are both pleasant and unpleasant things.

09:29.000 --> 09:32.000
Depending on what the person focuses on,

09:32.000 --> 09:36.000
depending on what he distinguishes from these aspects,

09:36.000 --> 09:40.000
this is a way of his accentuation of information.

09:40.000 --> 09:45.000
And if a person is all the time immersed in past failures,

09:45.000 --> 09:47.000
and you draw him future prospects,

09:47.000 --> 09:51.000
he does not hear you, because he is all there.

09:52.000 --> 09:56.000
If a person is immersed in all-time problems,

09:56.000 --> 10:01.000
here is the tax, here is the wrong payment from the bank,

10:01.000 --> 10:04.000
