During the year, when?

11:40.000 --> 11:45.000
December 31, January 1, October, when the financial year,

11:45.000 --> 11:49.000
this is a person who needs a clear indication of time, up to the hours.

11:49.000 --> 11:51.000
No matter how funny it sounds.

11:51.000 --> 11:55.000
Very often profitable contracts are broken

11:55.000 --> 11:59.000
precisely because I just ask you honestly,

11:59.000 --> 12:05.000
tell me how many weeks, months, years will I get the result?

12:05.000 --> 12:07.000
I need a number.

12:07.000 --> 12:13.000
And you start saying that I don't think it will take a long time.

12:13.000 --> 12:18.000
I'm not interested in these long names, long speeches,

12:18.000 --> 12:20.000
which we will talk about a little later.

12:20.000 --> 12:22.000
I'm interested in specifics.

12:22.000 --> 12:26.000
There are other people who are involved in time

12:26.000 --> 12:30.000
and in the sense that they do not notice it.

12:31.000 --> 12:33.000
These are the people who say,

12:33.000 --> 12:38.000
so, morning, well, good, we need to do something,

12:38.000 --> 12:42.000
oh, it's already lunch, okay, let's continue,

12:42.000 --> 12:44.000
oh, the worker is already finished,

12:44.000 --> 12:46.000
well, nothing, we'll do it tomorrow.

12:46.000 --> 12:48.000
These are people who, as they say,

12:48.000 --> 12:51.000
