12:51.000 --> 12:53.000
but these are the people who cannot be put down.

12:53.000 --> 12:55.000
These are not punctual people.

12:55.000 --> 12:58.000
I'm not saying that a person will not do something,

12:58.000 --> 13:00.000
that this person will not succeed.

13:00.000 --> 13:03.000
But this is a person for whom time is the main perspective.

13:03.000 --> 13:05.000
The main result can be for him.

13:05.000 --> 13:07.000
And it doesn't matter when I achieve it.

13:07.000 --> 13:10.000
Today or in 13 years.

13:10.000 --> 13:12.000
The main thing is that I have achieved it.

13:12.000 --> 13:14.000
And where was the time?

13:14.000 --> 13:16.000
We still live, we haven't died yet.

13:16.000 --> 13:21.000
If there is such a time,

13:21.000 --> 13:24.000
no matter what, and a person who is punctual,

13:24.000 --> 13:27.000
no matter how much,

13:27.000 --> 13:29.000
these people will never agree.

13:29.000 --> 13:33.000
The next element of the program is the so-called persuaders.

13:33.000 --> 13:41.000
For each person, it is always desirable to repeat something,

13:41.000 --> 13:44.000
to base something on something, to pay attention to something.

13:44.000 --> 13:50.000
Each of us reacts differently to these repetitions.

13:50.000 --> 13:55.000
In this regard, we can highlight several groups of persuaders,

13:55.000 --> 13:57.000
repetitions that need to be done.

13:57.000 --> 13:59.000
Persuaders can be based on intensity.

13:59.000 --> 14:03.000
Someone needs to constantly, intensely, persistently indicate.

14:03.000 --> 14:06.000
You have to do it because, because, because.

14:06.000 --> 14:09.000
And the more you are persistent,

14:09.000 --> 14:13.000
the more aggressive you will be to indicate,

14:13.000 --> 14:15.000
the more intense you will be doing it,

14:15.000 --> 14:17.000
the more a person will be convinced that,

14:17.000 --> 14:19.000
if you insist so,

14:19.000 --> 14:21.000
it means that you have already checked it,

14:21.000 --> 14:24.000
and it means that you are really ready to get down to business

14:24.000 --> 14:26.000
and are sure that the result will be.

14:26.000 --> 14:29.000
This is, let's say, from the section

14:29.000 --> 14:31.000
of impudence, the second part.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.000
But if you are so sure that you are saying,

14:33.000 --> 14:36.000
if you constantly demonstrate it,

14:36.000 --> 14:38.000
well, okay, let's try.

14:38.000 --> 14:44.000
But you understand that not everyone can be affected by this.

14:44.000 --> 14:50.000
Usually, if a person, well, let's say,

14:50.000 --> 14:54.000
is not very active, not very confident,

14:54.000 --> 14:57.000
not very ambitious, then intensity affects him.

14:57.000 --> 14:58.000
In fact, it's pressure.

14:58.000 --> 15:02.000
I press you in order to get the result I need.

15:02.000 --> 15:05.000
If a person is self-sufficient,

15:05.000 --> 15:09.000
then this intensity can have a completely different effect.

15:09.000 --> 15:13.000
Why are you pressing me, why are you not insisting?

15:13.000 --> 15:15.000
Why are you teaching me?

15:15.000 --> 15:18.000
And, accordingly, with such a person,

15:18.000 --> 15:21.000
to speak to such kind of persuaders is an absolutely

15:21.000 --> 15:25.000
correct way for the contract to be broken.

15:25.000 --> 15:27.000
For other people,

15:27.000 --> 15:32.000
the number of times of repetition is the persuader.

15:32.000 --> 15:38.000
If you talk a lot about this contract,

15:38.000 --> 15:40.000
if you bring recommendations,

15:40.000 --> 15:42.000
what are recommendations?

15:42.000 --> 15:45.000
There is one of the quantitative persuaders.

15:45.000 --> 15:48.000
The more recommendations you bring,

15:48.000 --> 15:55.000
the more it can be a sign that you can really be dealt with.

15:55.000 --> 15:58.000
And, accordingly, you see how many companies

15:58.000 --> 16:00.000
have interaction with your company,

16:00.000 --> 16:02.000
and they are all more or less satisfied,

16:02.000 --> 16:04.000
judging by the recommendations you gave me.

16:04.000 --> 16:09.000
In this case, this number indicates that you are repeating.

16:09.000 --> 16:12.000
But, again, as for persuaders,

16:12.000 --> 16:14.000
I want to draw your attention to the fact

16:14.000 --> 16:16.000
