16:31.000 --> 16:35.000
because it can be perceived against you.

16:36.000 --> 16:40.000
The next killer is purity.

16:40.000 --> 16:42.000
How often do you repeat?

16:42.000 --> 16:44.000
You can say every word,

16:44.000 --> 16:47.000
but my company has not let anyone down yet.

16:47.000 --> 16:50.000
You can say this at the beginning and at the end.

16:50.000 --> 16:52.000
You can say this once.

16:52.000 --> 16:54.000
It is perceived differently.

16:54.000 --> 16:57.000
If you are constantly cleaning,

16:57.000 --> 17:00.000
