17:22.000 --> 17:25.000
If, on the contrary, this person is convincing

17:25.000 --> 17:28.000
and acts only on the purity of repetition,

17:28.000 --> 17:31.000
then you really need to speak as often as possible.

17:31.000 --> 17:37.000
If this person is considered convincing as intensity,

17:37.000 --> 17:41.000
then here your purity will be an extra way

17:41.000 --> 17:44.000
