17:44.000 --> 17:46.000
The next killer is period.

17:46.000 --> 17:54.000
How often do you present evidence of what needs to be done?

17:54.000 --> 17:58.000
In this case, it can be about

17:58.000 --> 18:01.000
if you have given one argument,

18:01.000 --> 18:04.000
another argument, after each of these arguments,

18:04.000 --> 18:07.000
after completing a certain cycle of evidence

18:07.000 --> 18:09.000
in the presentation of your contract,

18:09.000 --> 18:13.000
