18:13.000 --> 18:15.000
this is a certain periodicity.

18:15.000 --> 18:19.000
It can be excessive, it can be insufficient.

18:19.000 --> 18:21.000
It all depends on the person again.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.000
What does he need?

18:22.000 --> 18:25.000
In frequent, periodic reinforcements,

18:25.000 --> 18:28.000
